lyrics:
[Verse]
As the stars fade into the dawn
And galaxies collide
We stand as witnesses to the wonders of the cosmic tide
In the echoes of eternity, our story will remain
A testament to the courage, the hope, and the endless refrain

[Chorus]
Farewell to the future of humanity
Our journey continues through eternity
With hearts ablaze, and souls set free
We transcend the bounds of what could ever be
